resources.string: You are about to begin the rating process of 50 images It is crucial that your rating will spread on all of the posiable ratings in order to provide the necesery security Please take your time and rate the images from 1 (Disliking the image) to 10(liking the image) At any time during the proccess you can return and update your ratings if you realize that your rating was wrong

You are about to start a new and experamental way to enter your device As we will try to recognize your by your preferance of diffrent images After rating our unique images we we will display a grid of images for you to select the most beutiful images Once you select the correct number of images we will check if it is in fact the top rated images As you can understand the rating phase is crucial in order to get the most of this app
